summary: Find secret items hidden through out cities that will boost your money.
descriptionHtml:
This mod aims to add a lot more loot that is actually worth something.

At the moment Riften is completed with over 50 new items to find through out the city inside buildings and outside, whether its the ratway or the shops to the fishery. Maybe a familiar man has something of value?

This mod will be updated with more cities each week and even villages and wilderness maybe adding random encounters with the chance to gain loot you could otherwise not earn til end game.
author: TheChode1
